      <title>What a nice surprise in the mail box (the actual physical mail box) this morning...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DVgKMLdgs7E/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/641227080_18573175873041826_9010150402792906253_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=106&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg0NjExNzg4MjA2MDc3NTY1Nw%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjEwODB4MTQ0MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=7XfmpKuRv9cQ7kNvwFnfCFq&amp;_nc_oc=AdoBEsahPD1ePCjBQaojamBXoO0G6-VFOU00ZP39KPGAhpN9l4yWHYnDZceGrnNdzl0&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=7&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=YHwjI611Ki3BfupsNTzLpg&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfzAM5yODekIyPXO4XakhCvEmqCuRvvUyLRZ35FuYOAGWw&amp;oe=69C9A0E1" alt="Instagram billede fra @sprngsmmr" /></p><p><strong>@sprngsmmr</strong></p><p>What a nice surprise in the mail box (the actual physical mail box) this morning. A copy of @grafikmagazin with a feature of the design we did for @nationalmuseet along with an interview. It’s a special museum theme this month and it’s an honor to be part of it.</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/641227080_18573175873041826_9010150402792906253_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=106&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg0NjExNzg4MjA2MDc3NTY1Nw%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjEwODB4MTQ0MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=7XfmpKuRv9cQ7kNvwFnfCFq&amp;_nc_oc=AdoBEsahPD1ePCjBQaojamBXoO0G6-VFOU00ZP39KPGAhpN9l4yWHYnDZceGrnNdzl0&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=7&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=YHwjI611Ki3BfupsNTzLpg&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfzAM5yODekIyPXO4XakhCvEmqCuRvvUyLRZ35FuYOAGWw&amp;oe=69C9A0E1" alt="Instagram billede fra @sprngsmmr" /></p><p><strong>@sprngsmmr</strong></p><p>What a nice surprise in the mail box (the actual physical mail box) this morning. A copy of @grafikmagazin with a feature of the design we did for @nationalmuseet along with an interview. It’s a special museum theme this month and it’s an honor to be part of it.</p>]]></content:encoded>
